Articles.Content:
Hello, everyone

I added a lot of Realism Overhaul mods via CKAN to a clean KSP 1.0.4, and tried a lot of time to start the game, but every time it stacked here: that is, the KSP has no response.

There are some differences in every start-up of loading items, but always: ModuleManager: 7567 patches loaded from cache.

Since it didn't crash with a crash-report, I can't provide that. But there is one of the latest crash report that might help:
